OL,3,CNo nudes please, we're naturalists!
OL,5,FThe Cumbria Nature Festival has issued
OL,6,Fa clarification after a "recent
OL,7,Fenquiry" raised confusion about its
OL,8,Fname.
OL,10,FAt least one person thought the event,
OL,11,Fwhich is aimed at naturalists, was
OL,12,Finstead aimed at naturists - or
OL,13,Fnudists, as they are also known.
OL,15,FThe event organisers posted on
OL,16,FFacebook: "Cumbria Nature Festival is
OL,17,Fprimarily aimed at NATURALISTS... not
OL,18,FNATURISTS.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/3
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
