PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1776791154
OL,3,CNo nudes please, we're naturalists!
OL,5,F"Whilst we aim to be as inclusive as
OL,6,Fpossible, and certainly do not judge
OL,7,Fanyone, we are aiming the event at
OL,8,Fwildlife enthusiasts.
OL,10,F"Please do dress appropriately."
OL,12,FThe Nature Festival's website says the
OL,13,Fevent is "dedicated to fostering a
OL,14,Fdeeper connection between people and
OL,15,Fthe natural world", and that it wants
OL,16,Fto celebrate the "incredible natural
OL,17,Fbeauty of Cumbria."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/3
