OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1776791154
OL,3,CNo nudes please, we're naturalists!
OL,5,FLive music, crafting workshops and on-
OL,6,Fsite camping are among the activities
OL,7,Fon offer during the event, which runs
OL,8,Ffrom the 8th - 10th May.
OL,10,FThe Cumbria Nature Festival's post
OL,11,Fended with a promise to reimburse any
OL,12,Fdisappointed nudists: "If anyone else
OL,13,Fhas booked in error, please contact us
OL,14,Fimmediately for a full refund."
